      "description": "Presenting scientific research geared toward a scientific audience.  Each student gives one 30-minute talk, one AGU-style 15-minute talk, and one poster presentation.  Students present their ongoing research and use the class as a forum to practice for upcoming talks in more formal settings.  Abstracts are prepared for each presentation and discussed in class.  Students provide comments, questions, encouragement, critiques, etc. on their peers&apos; presentations.",
